 * host: string containing host name or ip
 * user: user name to use to ssh into the host
 * description: optional string conatining description of host
 * reboot: optional true/false flag to indicate whether to reboot (true) or shutdown
 * defaults to shutdown
 * formats the data ready to be passed to notification node for OK/Cancel
*/
